              "docs": "Use the concentration of particulates of size less than 2.5\u00b5m in \u00b5g per cubic meter.\n  * All options from [Sensor](https://esphome.io/components/sensor/index.html#config-sensor).\n  \n  \n\n*See also: [The Grove - Laser PM2.5 Sensor (HM3301)](https://esphome.io/components/sensor/hm3301.html#configuration-variables)*",
